      "review_summary": "The branch adds a shared `extractToolResultText()` helper and applies it across OpenAI, Anthropic, Google/Gemini, and Mistral provider/transport conversion paths so structured non-image tool-result blocks are serialized as text.\n\nPR surface: Source +68, Tests +376. Total +444 across 14 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the narrower structured conversion path: current main filters tool results to text blocks in OpenAI Responses and active transport conversion, so structured non-image content can become empty before placeholder handling. The broader linked provider-failover/session-corruption behavior is not fully reproduced by this PR.",
